<span data-ttu-id="6285f-103">Negalite įrašyti el. laiškų "Outlook.com", bet galite juos išspausdinti PDF formatu, kurį galite įrašyti savo kompiuteryje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285f-103">You cannot save email messages in Outlook.com, but you can print them to a PDF which you can save on your PC.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="6285f-104">"Microsoft Print to PDF" įrankis, įtrauktas į "Windows 10", leidžia spausdinti bet kokį laišką tiesiogiai PDF formatu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285f-104">The Microsoft Print To PDF utility included in Windows 10 allows you to print any email message directly to a PDF.</span></span>

1. <span data-ttu-id="6285f-105">Pasirinkite laišką, kurį norite įrašyti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285f-105">Select the message you want to save.</span></span>
2. <span data-ttu-id="6285f-106">Pažymėti tris taškus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285f-106">Select the three dots</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="6285f-107">pranešimo viršuje ir pasirinkite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285f-107">at the top of the message and then select</span></span> <img src='data:image/png;base64,' />
 <span data-ttu-id="6285f-108">**Spausdinti**.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6285f-108">**Print**.</span></span>
